Titolo: Bud Spencer & Terence Hill: Slaps and Beans

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Bud Spencer & Terence Hill: Slaps and Beans is a side-scrolling beat 'em up game, with some elements of platform and minigames, developed by Trinity Team srls, it is the first official videogame inspired by the Italian duo of actors Bud Spencer and Terence Hill and released first in 2017 for PC and then ported in 2018 also for PlayStation 4, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 63
